_json.title: Simple And Pleated Dress in Black
_json.gridTitle: Simple And Pleated Dress in Black
_json.description: This black dress is classy and ultra-flattering on the female figure! It features sheer balloon sleeves and a sheer backing with a keyhole and button closure. The skirt is pleated, lined, flowy, and so stunning! This dress also has an adjustable tie detail at the waist. You'll love feeling empowered and so breathtaking in this piece. Light Weight Lined Sheer Sleeve Regular Sizes: Completely Sheer Back (see photos for example) Plus Sizes: Lined Back Functional Waist Tie 100% Polyester
